FOR THESE DAMNED DRINKS.

39:34.120 --> 39:35.520
GET OUT OF MY FACE.

39:35.520 --> 39:37.790
ALL RIGHT, LOOK, COME ON,
LET'S GET YOU TO A CAB.

39:37.790 --> 39:39.590
