40:32.320 --> 40:33.390
SO WHAT ARE WE DOING?

40:33.390 --> 40:36.250
HERE'S THE KEY.

40:36.250 --> 40:38.050
WHAT WE ALWAYS DO.

40:38.050 --> 40:41.120
