40:47.520 --> 40:49.250
ALL RIGHT.

40:49.250 --> 40:51.590
YOU COMING?

40:51.590 --> 40:55.090
NO.
I'M GONNA NEED AN ALIBI.

40:55.090 --> 40:56.220
