THAT SHE NEEDS TO GO HOME.

41:13.490 --> 41:14.750
CAN YOU GET YOUR HANDS
OFF OF ME?

41:14.750 --> 41:15.690
WHAT ARE YOU WEARING?

41:15.690 --> 41:17.190
